ğŸ›¡ï¸ 3. Security Layers
âœ… HTTPS enforced (HSTS)
âœ… Input validation (Zod or Joi)
âœ… SQL/NoSQL injection protection (via Prisma/Mongoose)
âœ… JWT signed with strong secret (JWT_SECRET from env)
âœ… Rate limiting (express-rate-limit or Vercel Edge Config)
âœ… File uploads scanned (if using Cloudflare R2/AWS S3)
âœ… Admin routes require role === 'admin'
